This vimrc is dilivered by http://wiki.csie.ncku.edu.tw/vim/vimrc.
And if you want to use monokai colorscheme, Plz download it from https://github.com/Bruceer/vim-monokai


set number
set ai
set cursorline
set bg=light
set tabstop=4
set shiftwidth=4
set ruler
set formatoptions+=r
set history=100
set incsearch

syntax on
syntax enable
colorscheme monokai

